script.name: !ship.cmd.freighttransfer.menu
script.description: Ship Command Preload: Ware selection for fetch freight
script.sourceplaintext:
$table.data = get global variable: name='cmd.ft.data' $pageid = 6020 if $table.data $target = $table.data['target'] $loaded.table = $table.data['loaded'] end
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] $drones = $a.ship -> get true amount of ware Freight Drone in cargo bay skip if $drones return null
$table.data = table alloc $loaded.table = table alloc $table.data['loaded'] = $loaded.table set global variable: name='cmd.ft.data' value=$table.data gosub sub.GetTarget return $input
else if $a.event == 'target.select' $target = $a.extra if $target == $a.ship $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104799 display game tip: text=$read.text delay=4000 START speak text: page=[Page.MiscVoice] id=135 priority=50 return [FALSE] end $table.data['target'] = $target gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.event == 'target' if $a.extra == Ship $text = read text: page=$pageid id=241 $input = create input: id='target.select', user input=Var/Ship owned by Player, refobj=$a.ship, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input else if $a.extra == Station $text = read text: page=$pageid id=241 $input = create input: id='target.select', user input=Var/Station owned by Player, refobj=$a.ship, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input else if $a.extra -> exists $target = $a.extra $table.data['target'] = $target gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input end
else if $a.event == 'menu' if $a.extra == 'start' return [TRUE] end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.TradeBarCh] $menu.id = $a.extra[0] $selection = $a.extra[1] $value = $a.extra[2] if $menu.id == 'menu' $table.data['current'] = $selection $table.data['current.tradebar'] = $value gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Selection] $menu.id = $a.extra[0] $selection = $a.extra[1] $value = $a.extra[2] if $menu.id == 'menu' $table.data['current'] = $value remove key 'current.tradebar' from table $table.data gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Select] $menu.id = $a.extra[0] $selection = $a.extra[1] if $menu.id == 'menu' if is datatype[ $selection ] == DATATYPE_WARE $value = $a.extra[3] if $value $loaded.table[$selection] = $value else remove key $selection from table $loaded.table end gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Cancelled] if $a.extra == 'target.select' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script !ship.cmd.freighttransfer.menu : Ship=$a.ship Event String=[MEvent.Start] Extra Data=null return $input end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Arguments] $ret = create new array, size=3, elements=$target, $loaded.table, [FALSE], null, null, null, null, null return $ret
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Finished] remove key 'current' from table $table.data remove key 'current.tradebar' from table $table.data set global variable: name='cmd.ft.data' value=null end
return null
sub.GetTarget: @ $menu = $a.ship -> call script !lib.input.cmd.target.player : Command=COMMAND_FREIGHT_TRANSFER Ships=[TRUE] a.stations=[TRUE] $text = read text: page=$pageid id=241 $title = get command name: command=COMMAND_FREIGHT_TRANSFER $input = create input: id='target' menu=$menu title=$title description=$text callback=null endsub
sub.DrawHeader: $text.coloumns = array alloc: size=6 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=-170 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$s.title $text.coloumns[0] = $text.col $read.text = read text: page=[Page.QMenus] id=130701 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=300 length=120 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.coloumns[1] = $text.col $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102518 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-130 length=30 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.coloumns[2] = $text.col $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102519 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-100 length=30 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.coloumns[3] = $text.col $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=706 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-50 length=50 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.coloumns[4] = $text.col $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=721 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=50 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.coloumns[5] = $text.col add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text.coloumns endsub
sub.DrawWare: $vol = get volume of ware $s.ware $text.coloumns = array alloc: size=7 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=-170 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$s.ware $text.coloumns[0] = $text.col $loaded.amt = $loaded.table[$s.ware] if $loaded.amt < 0 $ship.amt = $a.ship -> get amount of ware $s.ware in cargo bay $s.value = - $loaded.amt $len = linear interpolation: x1=0, x2=$ship.amt, y1=60, y2=0, value=$s.value if $len <= 0 $text = create custom menu string progress: width=60 progress=100% $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=300 length=60 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.coloumns[1] = $text.col else $text = create custom menu string progress: width=$len progress=0% $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=300 length=$len right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.coloumns[1] = $text.col $pos = 299 + $len $len = ( 60 - $len ) + 1 $text = create custom menu string progress: width=$len progress=100% $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$len right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text append $text.col to array $text.coloumns end $text = create custom menu string progress: width=60 progress=0% else $text = create custom menu string progress: width=60 progress=0% $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=300 length=60 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.coloumns[1] = $text.col $ship.max = $a.ship -> get cargo bay size $ship.amt = $a.ship -> get volume of ware $s.ware in cargo bay $target.amt = $target -> get amount of ware $s.ware in cargo bay $s.value = ( $loaded.amt * $vol ) + $ship.amt $percent = ( $s.value * 100 ) / $ship.max $text = create custom menu string progress: width=60 progress=$percent% end $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=360 length=60 right=[FALSE] colour=[MenuColour.Normal] text=$text $text.coloumns[2] = $text.col $text = convert number $vol to string $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-130 length=30 right=[TRUE] colour=[MenuColour.Normal] text=$text $text.coloumns[3] = $text.col $tc = get transport class of ware $s.ware $text = get short transport class name: class=$tc $ship.cantransport = $a.ship -> can transport ware $s.ware if $target -> is of class Ship skip if $target -> can transport ware $s.ware $ship.cantransport = [FALSE] end
if $ship.cantransport $text.colour = [MenuColour.Normal] else $text.colour = [MenuColour.Red] end $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-100 length=30 right=[TRUE] colour=$text.colour text=$text $text.coloumns[4] = $text.col $target.amt = $target -> get amount of ware $s.ware in cargo bay $ship.amt = $a.ship -> get volume of ware $s.ware in cargo bay if $target.amt OR $ship.amt $text.colour = [MenuColour.Normal] else $text.colour = [MenuColour.Red] end $text = convert number $target.amt to string $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-50 length=50 right=[TRUE] colour=$text.colour text=$text $text.coloumns[5] = $text.col $text = convert number $ship.amt to string $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=50 right=[TRUE] colour=$text.colour text=$text $text.coloumns[6] = $text.col
if $ship.cantransport AND ( $target.amt OR $ship.amt ) $ret = create menu return value: callback, value=$s.ware if $target -> get cargo bay size $freight.text = ' ' gosub sub.ComputeTotalTargetSpace $target.total = $target -> get cargo bay size $target.max = ( $target.total - $target.used ) / $vol else $target.max = $target -> get max amount of ware $s.ware that can be stored in cargo bay $target.total = $target.max $current.ware = $table.data['current'] $current.amt = $table.data['current.tradebar'] $target.used = $target.amt if $current.ware AND $current.ware == $s.ware do if is datatype[ $current.amt ] == DATATYPE_INT $target.used = $target.amt - $current.amt end end
if $target.max >= 10000 $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102540 else $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102510 end $text2 = convert number $target.used to string $text3 = convert number $target.total to string $freight.text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s/%s', $text, $text2, $text3, null, null
gosub sub.ComputeShipSpace $loaded.amt = $loaded.table[$s.ware] skip if $loaded.amt $loaded.amt = 0 $current.ware = $table.data['current'] $current.amt = $table.data['current.tradebar'] if $current.ware AND $current.ware == $s.ware if is datatype[ $current.amt ] == DATATYPE_INT $loaded.amt = $current.amt end end add transfer trade bar to menu: $menu, text=$text.coloumns, volume=$vol, current=$loaded.amt, station amount=$target.amt, station max=$target.max, ship amount=$ship.amt, ship free=$ship.free, ship used=$ship.used, return value=$ret $item = get last item in array: $menu $item = add menu trade bar text: $item id=[TradeBarText.InfoRight] text='%FREIGHT%' $item = add menu trade bar text: $item id=[TradeBarText.InfoLeft] text=$freight.text $target.name = $target -> get name $item = add menu trade bar text: $item id=[TradeBarText.Left1] text=$target.name $item = add menu trade bar text: $item id=[TradeBarText.Right1] text=$a.ship else set menu line option: $menu, selection colour=[MenuColour.Red] set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Red] $ret = create menu return value: disabled, id=$s.ware add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.coloumns returnvalue=$ret end endsub
sub.ComputeTotalTargetSpace: gosub sub.ComputeTargetSpace if $s.ware $loaded.amt = $loaded.table[$s.ware]
$current.ware = $table.data['current'] $current.amt = $table.data['current.tradebar'] if $current.ware AND $current.ware == $s.ware do if is datatype[ $current.amt ] == DATATYPE_INT $loaded.amt = $current.amt end
if $loaded.amt $next.ware.vol = get volume of ware $s.ware $next.ware.vol = $next.ware.vol * ( - $loaded.amt ) $target.free = $target.free - $next.ware.vol $target.used = $target.used + $next.ware.vol end end endsub
sub.ComputeTargetSpace: $target.free = $target -> get free volume of cargo bay $target.used = $target -> get total volume in cargo bay $next.ware = get next key: table=$loaded.table key=null while $next.ware if $next.ware != $s.ware $loaded.amt = $loaded.table[$next.ware] if $loaded.amt $next.ware.vol = get volume of ware $next.ware $next.ware.vol = $next.ware.vol * ( - $loaded.amt ) $target.free = $target.free - $next.ware.vol $target.used = $target.used + $next.ware.vol end end $next.ware = get next key: table=$loaded.table key=$next.ware end endsub
sub.ComputeShipSpace: $ship.free = $a.ship -> get free volume of cargo bay $ship.used = $a.ship -> get total volume in cargo bay $next.ware = get next key: table=$loaded.table key=null while $next.ware if $next.ware != $s.ware $loaded.amt = $loaded.table[$next.ware] if $loaded.amt $next.ware.vol = get volume of ware $next.ware $next.ware.vol = $next.ware.vol * $loaded.amt $ship.free = $ship.free - $next.ware.vol $ship.used = $ship.used + $next.ware.vol end end $next.ware = get next key: table=$loaded.table key=$next.ware end endsub
sub.DrawWareList: if size of array $s.array gosub sub.DrawHeader $s.array = sort array $s.array $s.i = 0 $s.size = size of array $s.array while $s.i < $s.size $s.ware = $s.array[$s.i] gosub sub.DrawWare inc $s.i = end end endsub
sub.BuildMenu: $pageid = 6022 $target = $table.data['target']
$menu = create custom menu array $menu.width = get menu width: widthtype=[MenuWidth.Big]
set menu option: $menu, icon=1 set menu option: $menu, remove main header=[TRUE] set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Big] set menu option: $menu, maximum infolines=20
$text = get command info: command=COMMAND_FREIGHT_TRANSFER add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text
$text.coloumns = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.QMenus] id=130701 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.coloumns[0] = $text.col $target.name = $target -> get name $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$target.name $text.coloumns[1] = $text.col $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-205 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$a.ship $text.coloumns[2] = $text.col add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$text.coloumns
$total.ship.volume = 0 $total.target.volume = 0 $done.any = [FALSE] $to.table = table alloc $from.table = table alloc $ware = get next key: table=$loaded.table key=null while $ware $ware.amt = $loaded.table[$ware] if $ware.amt $done.any = [TRUE] $ware.vol = get volume of ware $ware
if $ware.amt > 0 $to.table[$ware] = $ware.amt else $amt = - $ware.amt $from.table[$ware] = $amt end
$text.coloumns = array alloc: size=3 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=250 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$ware $text.coloumns[0] = $text.col if $ware.amt > 0 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text='-' else $amt = - $ware.amt $text = convert number $amt to string $amt = $amt * $ware.vol $total.target.volume = $total.target.volume + $amt $total.ship.volume = $total.ship.volume - $amt $text2 = convert number $amt to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s)', $text, $text2, null, null, null $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text end $text.coloumns[1] = $text.col if $ware.amt > 0 $text = convert number $ware.amt to string $amt = $ware.amt * $ware.vol $total.ship.volume = $total.ship.volume + $amt $total.target.volume = $total.target.volume - $amt $text2 = convert number $amt to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s)', $text, $text2, null, null, null $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-205 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text else $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-205 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text='-' end $text.coloumns[2] = $text.col
add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.coloumns end $ware = get next key: table=$loaded.table key=$ware end
if $done.any add info line section to menu: $menu
$text.coloumns = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$pageid id=100 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=250 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.coloumns[0] = $text.col $ship.used = $a.ship -> get total volume in cargo bay $ship.used = $ship.used + $total.ship.volume $text = convert number $ship.used to string $ship.max = $a.ship -> get cargo bay size $text2 = convert number $ship.max to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s/%s', $text, $text2, null, null, null $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-205 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.coloumns[1] = $text.col add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.coloumns
if $target -> get cargo bay size $target.used = $target -> get total volume in cargo bay $target.used = $target.used + $total.target.volume $text = convert number $target.used to string $target.max = $target -> get cargo bay size $text2 = convert number $target.max to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s/%s', $text, $text2, null, null, null $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text append $text.col to array $text.coloumns end
@ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !lib.trade.splitdrones : Ware Table=$to.table Drone Ship Type=null $size.1 = size of array $ret @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !lib.trade.splitdrones : Ware Table=$from.table Drone Ship Type=null $size.2 = size of array $ret $drones.needed = get maximum, $size.1, $size.2, null, null, null
$text.coloumns = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=$pageid id=101 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=250 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.coloumns[0] = $text.col $drones.got = $a.ship -> get amount of ware Freight Drone in cargo bay $text = sprintf: fmt='%s/%s', $drones.needed, $drones.got, null, null, null $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-205 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.coloumns[1] = $text.col $trips = $drones.needed / $drones.got do if $drones.needed mod $drones.got inc $trips = $read.text = read text: page=$pageid id=103 $text = sprintf: fmt='(%s: %s)', $read.text, $trips, null, null, null $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.coloumns[2] = $text.col add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.coloumns else $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=714 add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$read.text end
if $target -> is of class Factory $s.title = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=705 $s.array = $target -> get products gosub sub.DrawWareList
$s.title = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102521 $s.array = $target ->get station primary resources gosub sub.DrawWareList
if $target -> is of class Complex Hub $s.title = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=4256 $s.array = $target ->get complex intermediate wares gosub sub.DrawWareList else $s.title = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102522 $s.array = $target ->get station secondary resources gosub sub.DrawWareList end else $s.title = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=705 $s.array = $a.ship -> get tradeable ware array from ship if $target -> is of class Ship $ware.array = $target -> get tradeable ware array from ship else $ware.array = $target -> get tradeable ware array from station end $s.array = merge arrays, $s.array, $ware.array, null, null, null $s.array = convert array to table: $s.array, increment=[FALSE] remove key Freight Drone from table $s.array $s.array = get keys: table=$s.array gosub sub.DrawWareList end
$text = get command name: command=COMMAND_FREIGHT_TRANSFER add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text $text = read text: page=$pageid id=102 if $done.any add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue='start' else set menu line option: $menu, selection colour=[MenuColour.Red] set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Red] $ret = create menu return value: disabled, id='start' add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$ret end
$text = get command name: command=COMMAND_FREIGHT_TRANSFER $callback = [Callback.TradeBarCh] | [Callback.Selection] $input = create input: id='menu' menu=$menu title=$text description=$target callback=$callback endsub return null
